nodes.documentation:
DAO contract:
1. Collects investors money (ether) & allocate stakes
2. Keep track of investor contributions with stakes
3. Allow investors to transfer stakes
4. allow investment proposals to be created and voted
5. execute successful investment proposals (i.e send money)
